*/*      CALL TERMREL TO RELEASE TERMINAL                            */ 00287000

*                                                               01S0223 00290000
*POSTECB:                                                       01S0223 00291000
*   PROC OPTIONS(SAVE(14));         /* START OF SUBROUTINE   @ZA35513*/ 00292000
POSTECB  ST    @14,@SA00003                                     01S0223 00293000
*   RFY                                                         01S0224 00294000
*    (ASCBPTR,                                                  01S0224 00295000
*     ECBPTR,                                                   01S0224 00296000
*     ERRTNPTR) RSTD;               /* RESTRICT REGISTERS FOR USE       00297000
*                                      WITH POST MACRO       @ZA46161*/ 00298000
*   TSBPTR=TCASTSB;                 /* OBTAIN FIRST TSB ON TSB QUEUE    00299000
*                                                            @ZA46161*/ 00300000
         L     @09,CVTPTR                                       01S0225 00301000
         L     @09,TCASTPTR(,@09)                               01S0225 00302000
         L     TSBPTR,TCASTSB(,@09)                             01S0225 00303000
*   DO WHILE(TSBPTR¬=0&TSBASCB¬=WEUASCB);/* SEARCH TSB QUEUE FOR TSB    00304000
*                                      MATCHING USER MEMORY  @ZA46161*/ 00305000
         B     @DE00226                                         01S0226 00306000
@DL00226 DS    0H                                               01S0227 00307000
*     TSBPTR=TSBXFWD;               /* NEXT TSB ON TSB CHAIN @ZA46161*/ 00308000
         L     @09,TSBEXTNT(,TSBPTR)                            01S0227 00309000
         L     @09,TSBXFWD(,@09)                                01S0227 00310000
         LR    TSBPTR,@09                                       01S0227 00311000
*   END;                            /* END SEARCH TSB QUEUE  @ZA46161*/ 00312000
@DE00226 LTR   TSBPTR,TSBPTR                                    01S0228 00313000
         BZ    @DC00226                                         01S0228 00314000
         LR    @09,RPLREG                                       01S0228 00315000
         SL    @09,@CF02100                                     01S0228 00316000
         L     @08,TSBASCB-1(,TSBPTR)                           01S0228 00317000
         LA    @08,0(,@08)                                      01S0228 00318000
         C     @08,WEUASCB(,@09)                                01S0228 00319000
         BNE   @DL00226                                         01S0228 00320000

         END   IKTCASCX,(C'PLS2047',0702,80206)                         02305000
./  ADD  SSI=01920574,NAME=IKTCASOX
         TITLE '*** IKTCASOX: BIND ASYNCHRONOUS EXIT ***'               00001000
IKTCASOX CSECT ,                                                01S0001 00002000
@MAINENT DS    0H                                               01S0001 00003000
         USING *,@15                                            01S0001 00004000
         B     @PROLOG                                          01S0001 00005000
         DC    AL1(16)                                          01S0001 00006000
         DC    C'IKTCASOX  80.192'                              01S0001 00007000
         DROP  @15                                                      00008000
@PROLOG  BALR  @12,0                                            01S0001 00009000
@PSTART  DS    0H                                               01S0001 00010000
         USING @PSTART,@12                                      01S0001 00011000
         ST    @13,@SA00001+4                                   01S0001 00012000
         LA    @03,@SA00001                                     01S0001 00013000
         LR    @13,@03                                          01S0001 00014000
         PRINT OFF                                                      00015000
         PRINT ON                                                       00016000
*                                                               01S0144 00017000
*/********************************************************************/ 00018000
*/*                                                                  */ 00019000
*/* SEGMENT-                                                         */ 00020000
*/*      IKTCASOX                                                    */ 00021000
*/*                                                                  */ 00022000
*/* FUNCTION-                                                        */ 00023000
*/*      MAINLINE CODE.                                              */ 00024000
*/*                                                                  */ 00025000
*/********************************************************************/ 00026000
*                                                               01S0144 00027000
*   DO;                             /* BLOCK MAIN MAIN SEGMENT       */ 00028000
*/********************************************************************/ 00029000
*/*     INITIALIZE THE REGISTERS USED                                */ 00030000
*/********************************************************************/ 00031000
*                                                               01S0145 00032000
*     SAVREG14=REG14;               /* SAVE RETURN ADDRESS           */ 00033000
         LR    SAVREG14,REG14                                   01S0145 00034000
*     RFY                                                       01S0146 00035000
*       REG14 UNRSTD;               /* UNRESTRICT REGISTER 14        */ 00036000
*     RPLBASE=REG1;                 /* INSERT ADDRESS OF RPL IN TO      00037000
*                                      BASE REGISTER                 */ 00038000
         LR    RPLBASE,REG1                                     01S0147 00039000
*/****************************************************************** */ 00040000
*/*     ESTABLISH THE CONDITION OF THE REQUEST VIA CHECK             */ 00041000
*/********************************************************************/ 00042000
*                                                               01S0148 00043000
*     GENERATE CODE;                                            01S0148 00044000
         CHECK RPL=(RPLBASE)                                            00045000
*     RFY                                                       01S0149 00046000
*       RETCODE RSTD;               /* RESTRICT THE RETURN CODE 01S0149 00047000
*                                      REGISTER                      */ 00048000
*     DO WHILE(RETCODE¬=0|NIBCON='0'B);/* OPNDST FAILED      @ZM21166*/ 00049000
         B     @DE00150                                         01S0150 00050000
@DL00150 DS    0H                                               01S0151 00051000
*       WSMACRTC=RETCODE;           /* SAVE RETURN CODE              */ 00052000
         STC   RETCODE,WSMACRTC(,RPLBASE)                       01S0151 00053000
*       WSMACRSC=REG0;              /* SAVE REASON CODE              */ 00054000
         STC   REG0,WSMACRSC(,RPLBASE)                          01S0152 00055000
*       IF RETCODE=4&REG0=8 THEN    /* CHECK FOR A STORAGE SHORTAGE  */ 00056000
         C     RETCODE,@CF00043                                 01S0153 00057000
         BNE   @RF00153                                         01S0153 00058000
         C     REG0,@CF00035                                    01S0153 00059000
         BNE   @RF00153                                         01S0153 00060000
*         DO;                                                   01S0154 00061000
*           WSRETRY=WSRETRY+1;      /* INCREMENT COUNTER             */ 00062000
         LA    @14,1                                            01S0155 00063000
         SLR   @08,@08                                          01S0155 00064000
         IC    @08,WSRETRY(,RPLBASE)                            01S0155 00065000
         ALR   @14,@08                                          01S0155 00066000
         STC   @14,WSRETRY(,RPLBASE)                            01S0155 00067000
*           WSRETRYB='1'B;          /* TURN ON RETRY BIT             */ 00068000
         OI    WSRETRYB(RPLBASE),B'00001000'                    01S0156 00069000
*           IF WSRETRY>RETRYMAX THEN/* TEST FOR RETRY COUNTER   01S0157 00070000
*                                      EXCEEDED                      */ 00071000
         CLI   WSRETRY(RPLBASE),10                              01S0157 00072000
         BNH   @RF00157                                         01S0157 00073000
*             DO;                                               01S0158 00074000
*               CALL TERMREL;                                   01S0159 00075000
*                                                               01S0159 00076000
         BAL   @14,TERMREL                                      01S0159 00077000
*/*            LEAVE(MAIN)                                           */ 00078000
*                                                               01S0160 00079000
*               GOTO #BCM0005;      /* EXIT, NO MORE RETRIES @ZA35513*/ 00080000
         B     #BCM0005                                         01S0160 00081000
*             END;                                              01S0161 00082000
*           GENERATE CODE;                                      01S0162 00083000
*                                                               01S0162 00084000
@RF00157 DS    0H                                               01S0162 00085000
         EXECRPL RPL=(RPLBASE)                                          00086000
*/*        LEAVE(MAIN) ON(RETCODE=0)                                 */ 00087000
*                                                               01S0163 00088000
*           IF(RETCODE=0) THEN                                  01S0163 00089000
         LTR   RETCODE,RETCODE                                  01S0163 00090000
         BZ    @RT00163                                         01S0163 00091000
*             GOTO #BCM0005;        /* EXIT, GOOD INITIAL RETURN CODE   00092000
*                                                            @ZA35513*/ 00093000
*         END;                                                  01S0165 00094000
*       ELSE                        /* ERROR CODE NOT RETRYABLE      */ 00095000
*         DO;                                                   01S0166 00096000
         B     @RC00153                                         01S0166 00097000
@RF00153 DS    0H                                               01S0167 00098000
*           CALL TERMREL;           /* RELEASE THE TERMINAL          */ 00099000
         BAL   @14,TERMREL                                      01S0167 00100000
*/*        LEAVE(MAIN)                                               */ 00101000
*                                                               01S0168 00102000
*           GOTO #BCM0005;          /* EXIT, ERROR NOT RETRYABLE        00103000
*                                                            @ZA35513*/ 00104000
         B     #BCM0005                                         01S0168 00105000
*         END;                                                  01S0169 00106000
*     END;                          /* END OF LOOP                   */ 00107000
@RC00153 DS    0H                                               01S0170 00108000
@DE00150 SLR   @14,@14                                          01S0170 00109000
         CR    RETCODE,@14                                      01S0170 00110000
         BNE   @DL00150                                         01S0170 00111000

*/*            CHECK FOR NO TERMINAL TO BIND                         */ 00116000
*/****************************************************************** */ 00117000
*                                                               01S0171 00118000
*     IF REG0=0&RPLFDB2=9 THEN      /* CHECK RPL FEED BACK FIELDS    */ 00119000

*/*                                                                  */ 00137000

*/*      MEMREQ                                                      */ 00139000
*/*                                                                  */ 00140000

*                                      ELEMENT                       */ 00150000

*       QBASEREG=ADDR(TWAUACQH);    /* LOAD THE ADDRESS OF THE QUEUE    00159000
*                                      INTO A REGI ER                */ 00160000

*                                      WORK ELEMENT                  */ 00166000

*       WEREG=WORKBASE;             /* LOAD THE ADDRESS OF THE NEW      00168000

*       WECODE1T=MEMREQNM;          /* LOAD THE FUNCTION CODE INTO      00171000
*                                      THE WORK ELEMENT              */ 00172000

*       GENERATE CODE               /* INSERT ON QUEUE               */ 00174000
*           REFS(WENEXT);                                       02S0184 00175000
REDO     ST    QHREG,WENEXT(WEREG) STORE PRESENT WORK ELEMENT ADDRESS  *00176000
                              INTO NEW WORK ELEMENT                     00177000
         CS    QHREG,WEREG,0(QBASEREG) COMPARE AND SWAP INTO QUEUE     *00178000
                              ANCHOR                                    00179000
         BNE   REDO          DO IT UNTIL YOU GET IT RIGHT               00180000
*       RFY                                                     02S0185 00181000
*        (QBASEREG,                                             02S0185 00182000
*         QHREG,                                                02S0185 00183000
*         WEREG) UNRSTD;            /* FREE UP WORK REGS     @ZA35513*/ 00184000
*/********************************************************************/ 00185000
*/*            AFTER WORK ELEMENT IS ON THE CHAIN                    */ 00186000
*/*            POST TASK RESPONSIBLE FOR THE QUEUE                   */ 00187000
*/********************************************************************/ 00188000
*                                                               02S0186 00189000
*       RFY                                                     02S0186 00190000
*         REG4 RSTD;                /* RESTRICT WORK REGSITER        */ 00191000
*       REG4=ADDR(TWAUECB);         /* LOAD THE ADDRESS OF THE ECB      00192000
*                                      INTO A REGISTER               */ 00193000
         L     @14,CVTPTR                                       02S0187 00194000

*       GENERATE CODE;                                          02S0188 00198000
         POST  (4),X'0'                                                 00199000
*       RFY                                                     02S0189 00200000
*         REG4 UNRSTD;              /* FREE UP WORK REGISTER         */ 00201000
*     END;                          /* END OF SEGMENT        @ZA35513*/ 00202000
*/********************************************************************/ 00203000
*/* END OF SEGMENT                                                   */ 00204000
*/********************************************************************/ 00205000
*                                                               02S0191 00206000
*   END;                            /* END(MAIN)                     */ 00207000
*#BCM0005:                                                      01S0192 00208000
*   ;                               /* END OF MAIN SEGMENT           */ 00209000
#BCM0005 DS    0H                                               01S0193 00210000
*/********************************************************************/ 00211000
*/* THIS CODE IS ENTERED FROM ANY LEAVE(MAIN) MACRO INSTRUCTION.     */ 00212000
*/********************************************************************/ 00213000

*/*                                                                  */ 00231000
*/* FUNCTION-                                                        */ 00232000

*   WSRETRYB='1'B;                  /* INDICATE RETRY                */ 00241000
         OI    WSRETRYB(RPLBASE),B'00001000'                    01S0198 00242000
*/* CHECK CONDITIONS OF RPL                                          */ 00243000
*                                                               01S0199 00244000
*   IF RPLRTNCD=16&RPLFDB2=10 THEN  /* CHECK FOR ERROR IN VTAM       */ 00245000
         CLI   RPLRTNCD(RPLBASE),16                             01S0199 00246000

*       WSRETRYB='0'B;              /* INDICATE NO RETRY POSSIBLE    */ 00254000
         NI    WSRETRYB(RPLBASE),B'11110111'                    01S0202 00255000

*       RFY                                                     01S0205 00261000

./  ADD  SSI=02320504,NAME=IKTCAS00
         TITLE '***** IKTCAS00 - TCAS MAIN TASK *****'                  00001000
IKTCAS00 CSECT ,                                                   0001 00002000
@MAINENT DS    0H                                                  0001 00003000
         USING *,@15                                               0001 00004000
         B     @PROLOG                                             0001 00005000
         DC    AL1(16)                                             0001 00006000
         DC    C'IKTCAS00  80.232'                                 0001 00007000
         DROP  @15                                                      00008000
@PROLOG  STM   @14,@12,12(@13)                                     0001 00009000
         BALR  @12,0                                               0001 00010000
@PSTART  DS    0H                                                  0001 00011000
         USING @PSTART,@12                                         0001 00012000
         ST    @13,@SA00001+4                                      0001 00013000
         LA    @07,@SA00001                                        0001 00014000
         ST    @07,8(,@13)                                         0001 00015000
         LR    @13,@07                                             0001 00016000
*                                      ADDRESS                       */ 00017000
*                                                                  0051 00018000
*/********************************************************************/ 00019000
*/*                                                                  */ 00020000
*/* PROCEDURE-                                                       */ 00021000
*/*    IKTCAS00                                                      */ 00022000
*/*                                                                  */ 00023000
*/* FUNCTION-                                                        */ 00024000
*/*    MAINLINE CODE                                                 */ 00025000
*/*                                                                  */ 00026000
*/********************************************************************/ 00027000
*                                                                  0051 00028000
*   CALL MLSCPF;                    /* INVOKE START COMMAND        0051 00029000
*                                      PROCESSING                    */ 00030000
         BAL   @14,MLSCPF                                          0051 00031000
*MLSLT:                             /* BEGIN SELECT WE ROUTIN        */ 00032000
*   DO WHILE(TWASYNQH¬=0);          /* IS THERE WE                   */ 00033000
MLSLT    B     @DE00052                                            0052 00034000
@DL00052 DS    0H                                                  0053 00035000
*     RFY                                                          0053 00036000
*       WESTD BASED(TWASYNQH);      /* POINTS TO WE                  */ 00037000
*     R10=TWASYNQH;                 /* R10 PTR TO FIRST W.E.         */ 00038000
         L     @07,TWASYNQH(,TWAPTR)                               0054 00039000
         LR    R10,@07                                             0054 00040000
*     IF WECODE1T=TCML THEN         /* IS WE FOR MAINLINE            */ 00041000
         CLI   WECODE1T(@07),X'01'                                 0055 00042000
         BNE   @RF00055                                            0055 00043000
*       DO;                         /* YES                           */ 00044000
*         DO I=1 TO 8 BY 1          /* TRANSLATE FUNC CODE           */ 00045000
*               WHILE(WECODE1F¬=FUNCODE(I));/* TO ROUTINE NUMBER     */ 00046000
         LA    I,1                                                 0057 00047000
@DL00057 L     @07,TWASYNQH(,TWAPTR)                               0057 00048000
         LA    @05,FUNCODE-1(I)                                    0057 00049000
         CLC   WECODE1F(1,@07),0(@05)                              0057 00050000
         BE    @DC00057                                            0057 00051000
*         END;                                                     0058 00052000
         AL    I,@CF00062                                          0058 00053000
         C     I,@CF00060                                          0058 00054000
         BNH   @DL00057                                            0058 00055000
@DC00057 DS    0H                                                  0059 00056000
*         IF I>0&I<8 THEN           /* CHECK VALID ROUTINE           */ 00057000
         LTR   I,I                                                 0059 00058000
         BNP   @RF00059                                            0059 00059000
         C     I,@CF00060                                          0059 00060000
         BNL   @RF00059                                            0059 00061000
*           DO;                     /* YES                           */ 00062000
*             MLWA1=WECODE1;        /* RETAIN WE CODE                */ 00063000
         L     @07,TWASYNQH(,TWAPTR)                               0061 00064000
         MVC   MLWA1(2),WECODE1(@07)                               0061 00065000
*             CALL FUNCTION;        /* CALL THE FUNCTION             */ 00066000
         LR    @07,I                                               0062 00067000
         SLA   @07,2                                               0062 00068000
         L     @15,FUNADD-4(@07)                                   0062 00069000
         BALR  @14,@15                                             0062 00070000
*             IF MLWA1¬=WECODE1 THEN/* IS SAME WE                    */ 00071000
         L     @07,TWASYNQH(,TWAPTR)                               0063 00072000
         CLC   MLWA1(2),WECODE1(@07)                               0063 00073000
         BNE   @RT00063                                            0063 00074000
*               GOTO MLSLTEND;      /* NO PROCESS AGAIN              */ 00075000
*           END;                                                   0065 00076000
*       END;                                                       0066 00077000
*     ELSE                          /* NOT FOR MAINLINE              */ 00078000
*       IF WECODE1T=TCVI THEN       /* IS IT FOR VTAM INT            */ 00079000
         B     @RC00055                                            0067 00080000
@RF00055 L     @07,TWASYNQH(,TWAPTR)                               0067 00081000
         CLI   WECODE1T(@07),X'02'                                 0067 00082000
         BNE   @RF00067                                            0067 00083000
*         DO;                       /* YES                           */ 00084000
*           R1=ADDR(TWAVECB);       /* GET ECB ADDR                  */ 00085000
         LA    R1,TWAVECB(,TWAPTR)                                 0069 00086000
*           GEN(POST (1));          /* ISSUE POST                    */ 00087000
         POST (1)                                                       00088000
*           GOTO MLWAIT;            /* GOTO WAIT                     */ 00089000
         B     MLWAIT                                              0071 00090000
*         END;                                                     0072 00091000
*       ELSE                        /* NOT VTAM                      */ 00092000
*         IF WECODE1T=TCUI THEN     /* IS IT FOR USER INT            */ 00093000
@RF00067 L     @07,TWASYNQH(,TWAPTR)                               0073 00094000
         CLI   WECODE1T(@07),X'03'                                 0073 00095000
         BNE   @RF00073                                            0073 00096000
*           DO;                     /* YES                           */ 00097000
*             R1=ADDR(TWAUECB);     /* GET ECB ADDR                  */ 00098000
         LA    R1,TWAUECB(,TWAPTR)                                 0075 00099000
*             GEN(POST (1));        /* ISSUE POST                    */ 00100000
         POST (1)                                                       00101000
*             GOTO MLWAIT;          /* GOTO WAIT                     */ 00102000
         B     MLWAIT                                              0077 00103000
*           END;                                                   0078 00104000
*         ELSE                      /* NOT USER                      */ 00105000
*           IF WECODE1T=TCCI THEN   /* IS IT FOR CON COMM            */ 00106000
@RF00073 L     @07,TWASYNQH(,TWAPTR)                               0079 00107000
         CLI   WECODE1T(@07),X'04'                                 0079 00108000
         BNE   @RF00079                                            0079 00109000
*             DO;                   /* YES                           */ 00110000
*               R1=ADDR(TWACECB);   /* GET ECB ADDR                  */ 00111000
         LA    R1,TWACECB(,TWAPTR)                                 0081 00112000
*               GEN(POST (1));      /* ISSUE POST                    */ 00113000

*/*                                                                  */ 01128000
*/* SUBPROCEDURE-                                                    */ 01129000
*/*    MLEOT                                                         */ 01130000
*/*                                                                  */ 01131000
*/* FUNCTION-                                                        */ 01132000
*/*    MAINLINE TASK TERMINATION                                     */ 01133000
*/*                                                                  */ 01134000
*/* INPUT : R10=ADDRESS OF WE OR ZERO                                */ 01135000
*/*         R8=FUNCTION CODE: ABEND OR NORMAL END IF R10=0           */ 01136000
*/*         R9 =TERMINATION REASON CODE IF R10=0                     */ 01137000
*/*                                                                  */ 01138000
*/* THIS ROUTINE GENERATES CODE TO NORMAL END OR                     */ 01139000
*/* ABEND THE TASK. THE CONTROL DOES NOT RETURN TO                   */ 01140000
*/* MAINLINE .                                                       */ 01141000
*/*                                                                  */ 01142000
*/********************************************************************/ 01143000
*                                                                  0437 01144000
*MLEOT:                                                            0437 01145000
*   PROC OPTIONS(NOSAVE,NOSAVEAREA);                               0437 01146000
MLEOT    DS    0H                                                  0438 01147000
*   IF R10¬=0 THEN                  /* IS THERE WE PASSED            */ 01148000
         LTR   R10,R10                                             0438 01149000
         BZ    @RF00438                                            0438 01150000
*     DO;                           /* YES                           */ 01151000
*       RFY                                                        0440 01152000
*         WESTD BASED(R10);         /* GET WE BASE                   */ 01153000
*       R9=WERC;                    /* RETURN CODE                   */ 01154000
         LH    R9,WERC(,R10)                                       0441 01155000
         N     R9,@CF01700                                         0441 01156000
*       R8=WECODE1F;                /* WHAT TYPE OF END              */ 01157000
         SLR   R8,R8                                               0442 01158000
         IC    R8,WECODE1F(,R10)                                   0442 01159000
*     END;                          /* REASON CODE                   */ 01160000
*   IF TWAPTR¬=0 THEN               /* IF THERE IS TWA               */ 01161000
@RF00438 LTR   TWAPTR,TWAPTR                                       0444 01162000
         BZ    @RF00444                                            0444 01163000
*     TWARSON=R9;                   /* YES STORE REASON CODE         */ 01164000
         STH   R9,TWARSON(,TWAPTR)                                 0445 01165000
*   MLWA22=R9;                      /* USE LAST BYTE AS RETURN       */ 01166000
@RF00444 STC   R9,MLWA22                                           0446 01167000
*   R9=MLWA22;                      /* CODE AND REASON CODE          */ 01168000
         SLR   @05,@05                                             0447 01169000
         IC    @05,MLWA22                                          0447 01170000
         LR    R9,@05                                              0447 01171000
*   IF R8=FCMLAT THEN               /* IS IT ABEND                   */ 01172000
         C     R8,@CF01460                                         0448 01173000
         BNE   @RF00448                                            0448 01174000
*     DO;                           /* YES                           */ 01175000
*       R1=2;                       /* MSG 2                         */ 01176000
         LA    R1,2                                                0450 01177000
*       CALL MSGBLK;                /* CALL MSG BLOCK GET M          */ 01178000
         L     @15,TWAMSG(,TWAPTR)                                 0451 01179000
         BALR  @14,@15                                             0451 01180000
*       R8=R1->MLWA3;               /* GET LENGTH                    */ 01181000
         L     R8,MLWA3(,R1)                                       0452 01182000
*       R1=R1+4;                    /* SKIP LEN FIELD                */ 01183000
         AL    R1,@CF00080                                         0453 01184000
*       MSGTXT=R1->AREA(1:R8);      /* MOVE MSG OUT                  */ 01185000
         MVI   MSGTXT+1,C' '                                       0454 01186000
         MVC   MSGTXT+2(98),MSGTXT+1                               0454 01187000
         LR    @05,R8                                              0454 01188000
         BCTR  @05,0                                               0454 01189000
         EX    @05,@SM01694                                        0454 01190000
*       CVD(R9,MLWAD);              /* FOR MSG TERM REASON           */ 01191000
         CVD   R9,MLWAD                                            0455 01192000
*       GEN;                                                       0456 01193000
         UNPK  MSGTXT+45(4),MLWAD  UNPACK                               01194000
         OI    MSGTXT+48,X'F0'     PRINTABLE LAST CHAR                  01195000
         WTO   MF=(E,MSGTXT)       SEND TERMINATING MSG                 01196000
         LR    R15,R9              REG 15 REASON              @ZA26725  01197000
         ABEND X'0AC',DUMP,,SYSTEM    ISSUE SYSTEM ABEND                01198000
*     END;                                                         0457 01199000
*   GEN;                                                           0458 01200000
@RF00448 DS    0H                                                  0458 01201000

*   GEN;                                                           0459 01203000
*                                          /* NO NORMAL TERM        */  01204000
         L     13,4(13)                LOAD SAVE AREA ADDR              01205000

./  ADD  SSI=02320505,NAME=IKTCAS20
         TITLE 'IKTCAS20 - VTAM INTERFACE DRIVER'                       00001000
IKTCAS20 CSECT ,                                                   0001 00002000
@MAINENT DS    0H                                                  0001 00003000
         USING *,@15                                               0001 00004000
         B     @PROLOG                                             0001 00005000
         DC    AL1(16)                                             0001 00006000
         DC    C'IKTCAS20  80.232'                                 0001 00007000
         DROP  @15                                                      00008000
@PROLOG  STM   @14,@12,12(@13)                                     0001 00009000
         BALR  @12,0                                               0001 00010000
@PSTART  DS    0H                                                  0001 00011000
         USING @PSTART,@12                                         0001 00012000
         ST    @13,@SA00001+4                                      0001 00013000
         LA    @14,@SA00001                                        0001 00014000
         ST    @14,8(,@13)                                         0001 00015000
         LR    @13,@14                                             0001 00016000
         EJECT                                                          00017000
*/********************************************************************/ 00018000
*/*                                                                  */ 00019000
*/*        THIS ROUTINE MANIPULATES THE QUEUES  ACCORDING TO         */ 00020000
*/*        THE PRIORITY OF THE QUEUES :                              */ 00021000
*/*            SYNCHRONOUS QUEUE                                     */ 00022000
*/*            TPEND QUEUE                                           */ 00023000
*/*            TERMINAL HANDLING QUEUE - GLOBAL                      */ 00024000
*/*            TERMINAL HANDLING QUEUE - LOCAL                       */ 00025000
*/*                                                                  */ 00026000
*/********************************************************************/ 00027000
*    /*                                                              */ 00028000
*    /*      ESTABLISH TCAS WORK AREA ADDRESSIBILITY AND SET         */ 00029000
*    /*      FOOTPRINT FOR ESTAI EXIT ROUTINE BY STORE DRIVER        */ 00030000
*    /*      FUNCTION CODE WITHOUT RETRY ADDRESS. THAT MEANS         */ 00031000
*    /*      ESTAI EXIT WILL ABEND THE TASK WITHOUT RETRY.           */ 00032000
*    /*                                                              */ 00033000
*      TWAPTR=R1 ;                     /* LOAD TWA ADDR PASSED IN R1 */ 00034000
         LR    TWAPTR,R1                                           0017 00035000
*      IKTWAPTR=TWAPTR ;               /* STORE TWA PTR              */ 00036000
         ST    TWAPTR,IKTWAPTR                                     0018 00037000
*      TCASTPTR=TWATCAST ;             /* TCAST POINTER              */ 00038000
         L     TCASTPTR,TWATCAST(,TWAPTR)                          0019 00039000
*      TWAVEIFC(1)=FCVIDI ;            /* SET FOOTPRINT FOR ESTAI    */ 00040000
         MVI   TWAVEIFC(TWAPTR),X'01'                              0020 00041000
*      TCASTTQH=0 ;                    /* INITIALIZE TO ZERO         */ 00042000
         SLR   @07,@07                                             0021 00043000
         ST    @07,TCASTTQH(,TCASTPTR)                             0021 00044000
*      SWITCH='00'X ;                  /* INITIALIZE SWITCH          */ 00045000
         MVI   SWITCH,X'00'                                        0022 00046000
*      DO WHILE (SWWAIT='0'B) ;        /* LOOP UNTIL BYPASS WAIT     */ 00047000
         B     @DE00023                                            0023 00048000
@DL00023 DS    0H                                                  0024 00049000
*      DO WHILE (SWPRQS='0'B) ;        /* LOOP UNTIL BYPASS PROCESS  */ 00050000
         B     @DE00024                                            0024 00051000
@DL00024 DS    0H                                                  0025 00052000
*                                      /* THE QUEUES                 */ 00053000
*      DO WHILE (SWPRTPEQ='0'B);       /* LOOP UNTIL BYPASS PROCESS  */ 00054000
         B     @DE00025                                            0025 00055000
@DL00025 DS    0H                                                  0026 00056000
*                                      /* THE TPEND QUEUE            */ 00057000
*      /*                                                            */ 00058000
*      /*    PROCESS  SYNCHRONOUS  QUEUE                             */ 00059000
*    /*                                                              */ 00060000
*      DO WHILE (TWASYNQH¬=0 &         /* LOPP WHILE Q IS NOT EMPTY  */ 00061000
*                SWPRQS='0'B ) ;       /*   AND NOT TO BE BYPASSED   */ 00062000
         B     @DE00026                                            0026 00063000
@DL00026 DS    0H                                                  0027 00064000
*      RFY WESTD BASED(TWASYNQH);      /* BASED ON FIRST W.E. ON Q   */ 00065000
*      R10=TWASYNQH ;                  /* R10 PTR TO FIRST W.E.      */ 00066000
         L     @07,TWASYNQH(,TWAPTR)                               0028 00067000
         LR    R10,@07                                             0028 00068000
*      SWDEQ='0'B ;                    /* INITIALIZE DEQ BYPASS BIT  */ 00069000
         NI    SWDEQ,B'11101111'                                   0029 00070000
*      IF WECODE1T=TCVI                /* IS THIS W.E. FOR VI SUBTASK*/ 00071000
*         THEN DO ;                    /* YES, PROCESS               */ 00072000
         CLI   WECODE1T(@07),X'02'                                 0030 00073000
         BNE   @RF00030                                            0030 00074000
*        IF WECDMAF=FCVIACB            /* IS THIS ACB CONTROL FUNCT  */ 00075000
*            THEN DO ;                 /* YES, PROCESS               */ 00076000
         TM    WECDMAF(@07),B'00010000'                            0032 00077000
         BNO   @RF00032                                            0032 00078000
         TM    WECDMAF(@07),B'11100000'                            0032 00079000
         BNZ   @RF00032                                            0032 00080000
*            WA2=WECODE1  ;            /* RETAIN FUNCTION CODE       */ 00081000
         MVC   WA2(2),WECODE1(@07)                                 0034 00082000
*            CALL IKTCAS21 ;           /* CALL ACB CONTROL FUNCTION  */ 00083000
         L     @15,@CV00307                                        0035 00084000
         BALR  @14,@15                                             0035 00085000
*            IF WA2¬=WECODE1           /* IF THE FUNCTION CODE CHANGE*/ 00086000
*               THEN SWDEQ='1'B ;      /* DONT DEQ,SET BYPASS BIT ON */ 00087000
         L     @07,TWASYNQH(,TWAPTR)                               0036 00088000
         CLC   WA2(2),WECODE1(@07)                                 0036 00089000
         BE    @RF00036                                            0036 00090000
         OI    SWDEQ,B'00010000'                                   0037 00091000
*            END;                                                  0038 00092000
*            ELSE                      /* NOT ACB CONTROL FUNCTION   */ 00093000
*              IF WECODE1F=FCVIDE      /* IS THIS EOT W.E.           */ 00094000
*                 THEN DO ;            /* YES                        */ 00095000
         B     @RC00032                                            0039 00096000
@RF00032 L     @07,TWASYNQH(,TWAPTR)                               0039 00097000
         CLI   WECODE1F(@07),X'03'                                 0039 00098000
         BNE   @RF00039                                            0039 00099000
*                 SWPRTPEQ='1'B ;      /* BYPASS PROCESS TPEND  Q    */ 00100000
*                 SWPRQS='1'B ;        /* BYPASS ALL THE QUEUES      */ 00101000
*                 SWWAIT='1'B;         /* BYPASS WAIT                */ 00102000
         OI    SWPRTPEQ,B'11100000'                                0043 00103000
*                 END ;                                            0044 00104000
*         END ;                                                    0045 00105000
*         ELSE                         /* W.E. IS FOR OTHER TASK     */ 00106000
*           IF WECODE1T=TCML           /* IS THIS W.E. FOR MAIN TASK */ 00107000
*              THEN DO ;               /* YES                        */ 00108000
         B     @RC00030                                            0046 00109000
@RF00030 L     @07,TWASYNQH(,TWAPTR)                               0046 00110000
         CLI   WECODE1T(@07),X'01'                                 0046 00111000
         BNE   @RF00046                                            0046 00112000
*              RFY (R14,R15,R0,R1) RSTD  /* RESTRICT PARA REG*/ ;  0048 00113000
*              R8=ADDR(TWAMECB);       /* MAIN TASK ECB ADDR         */ 00114000
         LA    R8,TWAMECB(,TWAPTR)                                 0049 00115000
*              GEN ;                                               0050 00116000
         POST  (R8)                   POST MAIN TASK                    00117000
*              RFY (R14,R15,R0,R1) UNRSTD /*UNRESTRI PARA R */ ;   0051 00118000
*              SWDEQ='1'B ;           /* BYPASS DEQ THE W.E.        */  00119000
*              SWPRTPEQ='1'B;          /* BYPASS PROCESS TPEND Q     */ 00120000
*              SWPRQS='1'B ;          /* BYPASS PROCESS ALL QS      */  00121000
         OI    SWDEQ,B'01110000'                                   0054 00122000
*              END;                                                0055 00123000
*              ELSE                    /* NOT MAIN TASK              */ 00124000
*                IF WECODE1T=TCUI      /* IS THIS USER INT SU@YM03216*/ 00125000
*                   THEN DO ;          /* YES                        */ 00126000
         B     @RC00046                                            0056 00127000
@RF00046 L     @07,TWASYNQH(,TWAPTR)                               0056 00128000
         CLI   WECODE1T(@07),X'03'                                 0056 00129000
         BNE   @RF00056                                            0056 00130000
*                   RFY (R14,R15,R0,R1) RSTD  /* RESTRICT PARA REG*/ ;  00131000
*                   R8=ADDR(TWAUECB) ; /* USER INT SUBTASK ECB ADDR  */ 00132000
         LA    R8,TWAUECB(,TWAPTR)                                 0059 00133000
*                   GEN ;                                          0060 00134000
         POST  (R8)                   POST USER INT SUBTASK             00135000
*                   RFY (R14,R15,R0,R1) UNRSTD /*UNRESTRI PARA R */ ;   00136000
*                   SWDEQ='1'B ;       /* BYPASS DEQ W.E.            */ 00137000
*                   SWPRTPEQ='1'B ;    /* BYPASS PROCESS TPEND Q     */ 00138000
*                   SWPRQS='1'B ;      /* BYPASS PROCESS ALL QS      */ 00139000
         OI    SWDEQ,B'01110000'                                   0064 00140000
*                   END ;                                          0065 00141000
*                   ELSE               /* NOT USER INT SUBTASK       */ 00142000
*                   IF WECODE1T=TCCI   /* IS THIS CON COMM SUBTASK   */ 00143000
*                      THEN DO ;       /* YES                        */ 00144000
         B     @RC00056                                            0066 00145000
@RF00056 L     @07,TWASYNQH(,TWAPTR)                               0066 00146000
         CLI   WECODE1T(@07),X'04'                                 0066 00147000
         BNE   @RF00066                                            0066 00148000
*                      RFY (R14,R15,R0,R1) RSTD  /* RESTRICT PARA REG*/ 00149000
*;                                                                 0068 00150000
*                      R8=ADDR(TWACECB); /* CON COMM SUBTASK ECB ADDR*/ 00151000
         LA    R8,TWACECB(,TWAPTR)                                 0069 00152000
*                      GEN ;                                       0070 00153000
         POST  (R8)                   POST CON COMM SUBTASK             00154000
*                      RFY (R14,R15,R0,R1) UNRSTD /*UNRESTRI PARA R */  00155000
*                      SWDEQ='1'B ;    /* BYPASS DEQ W.E.            */ 00156000
*                      SWPRTPEQ='1'B ; /* BYPASS PROCESS TPEND Q     */ 00157000
*                      SWPRQS='1'B ;   /* BYPASS PROCESS ALL QS      */ 00158000
         OI    SWDEQ,B'01110000'                                   0074 00159000
*                      END ;                                       0075 00160000
*      IF SWDEQ='0'B                   /* IS DEQ W.E. NOT BYPASS     */ 00161000
*         THEN DO ;                    /* NO, GO AHEAD DEQ           */ 00162000
@RF00066 DS    0H                                                  0076 00163000
@RC00056 DS    0H                                                  0076 00164000
@RC00046 DS    0H                                                  0076 00165000
@RC00030 TM    SWDEQ,B'00010000'                                   0076 00166000
         BNZ   @RF00076                                            0076 00167000
*         R8=ADDR(TWASYNQH) ;          /* SYNCHRONOUS Q HEADER ADDR  */ 00168000
         LA    R8,TWASYNQH(,TWAPTR)                                0078 00169000
*         GEN SETS(TWASYNQH);          /* COMPARE SWAP TO DEQ        */ 00170000
         L     10,0(8)                LOAD ADDR OF FIRST W.E.           00171000
CSLOOP   L     9,4(10)                LOAD ADDR OF NEXT W.E.            00172000
         CS    10,9,0(8)              DEQ FIRST W.E.                    00173000
         BNE   CSLOOP                 LOOP IF NOT SUCCESSFUL            00174000
*         IF R9=0                      /* IS THIS LAST W.E. ON THE Q */ 00175000
*            THEN DO ;                 /* YES, POST ALL OTHER SUBTASK*/ 00176000
         LTR   R9,R9                                               0080 00177000
         BNZ   @RF00080                                            0080 00178000
*            R8=ADDR(TWAUECB) ;        /* ADDR OF USER INT ECB       */ 00179000
         LA    R8,TWAUECB(,TWAPTR)                                 0082 00180000
*            R9=ADDR(TWACECB) ;        /* ADDR OF CON COMM ECB       */ 00181000
         LA    R9,TWACECB(,TWAPTR)                                 0083 00182000
*            RFY (R14,R15,R0,R1) RSTD  /* RESTRICT PARA REG*/ ;    0084 00183000
*            GEN ;                                                 0085 00184000
         POST  (R8)                   POST USER INT SUBTASK             00185000
         POST  (R9)                   POST CON COMM SUBTASK             00186000
*            RFY (R14,R15,R0,R1) UNRSTD /*UNRESTRI PARA R */ ;     0086 00187000
*            END ;                                                 0087 00188000
*         END ;                                                    0088 00189000
@RF00080 DS    0H                                                  0089 00190000
*      END ;                           /* END OF SYNC Q PROCESS LOOP */ 00191000

         BZ    @DL00026                                            0089 00197000
@DC00026 DS    0H                                                  0090 00198000
*    /*                                                              */ 00199000
*    /*      PROCESS  ASYNCHRONOUS  QUEUES                           */ 00200000
*    /*                                                              */ 00201000
*/*                                                                  */ 00202000
*/*            PROCESS  TPEND QUEUE                                  */ 00203000
*/*                                                                  */ 00204000
*      IF SWPRTPEQ='0'B                /* NOT TO BYPASS TPEND Q PROC */ 00205000
*         THEN DO ;                    /* NO, GO AHEAD PROCESS       */ 00206000

*         END ;                                                    0103 00234000
*      END ;                           /* END OF PROCESS TPEND Q LOOP*/ 00235000

         BNZ   @RF00106                                            0106 00244000
*/*                                                                  */ 00245000
*/*          PROCESS  TERMINAL HANDLING  QUEUE - GLOBAL              */ 00246000
*/*            THE WORK ELEMENT IS THE REQUEST FROM TSO              */ 00247000
*/*            USER ADDRESS SPACE                                    */ 00248000
*/*                                                                  */ 00249000
*         RFY R1 RSTD ;                /* SET PARAMETER REG          */ 00250000

*/*          PROCESS  TERMINAL  HANDLING  QUEUE - LOCAL              */ 00272000
*/*                                                                  */ 00273000
*         R1=ADDR(TWAVTHQH) ;          /* ADDR OF Q HEADER TO BE DEQ */ 00274000
@RF00111 LA    R1,TWAVTHQH(,TWAPTR)                                0119 00275000
*         CALL DEQASYN ;               /* CALL DEQ ROUTINE           */ 00276000

*    /*                                                              */ 00310000
*    /*        WAIT  FOR  WORK - WAIT ON AN ECB. IF POSTED,          */ 00311000
*    /*                          MEANS MORE WORK AND W.E. ARE QUEUED */ 00312000
*    /*                                                              */ 00313000
*      IF SWWAIT='0'B                  /* WAIT NOT TO BE BYPASSED    */ 00314000

*    /*                                                              */ 00334000
*    /*        ROUTINE TO DE-CHAIN THE LAST WE ON ASYCHRONOUS QUEUE  */ 00335000
*    /*                                                              */ 00336000
*    /*        INPUT: R1 ADDRESS OF ASY QUEUE                        */ 00337000
*    /*               R14 RETURN ADDR                                */ 00338000
*    /*               R13 A SAVE AREA CONTAINS AT LEAST 6 WORDS BUT  */ 00339000
*    /*                   ONLY LAST 4 WORDS TO BE USED               */ 00340000
*    /*                                                              */ 00341000
*    /*        OUTPUT: R1 ADDRESS OF THE WE DE-CHAINED OR ZERO       */ 00342000
*    /*                   IF ZERO, ASY QUEUE WAS EMPTY               */ 00343000
*    /*                                                              */ 00344000
*DEQASYN : PROC OPTIONS(SAVE(R14),NOSAVEAREA) ;                    0144 00345000
@EL00001 L     @13,4(,@13)                                         0144 00346000
@EF00001 DS    0H                                                  0144 00347000
@ER00001 LM    @14,@12,12(@13)                                     0144 00348000
         BR    @14                                                 0144 00349000
DEQASYN  ST    @14,12(,@13)                                        0144 00350000
*      RFY R1 RSTD ;                                               0145 00351000
*      R9=0  ;                         /* ZERO FOR COMPARE SWAP      */ 00352000

*                                      /* INSTRUCTION TO DEQ W.E.    */ 00354000
*      SW='1'B ;                       /* SET SWITCH                 */ 00355000

*      DO WHILE (SW='1'B ) ;            /* LOOP UNTIL CS WORK        */ 00357000

@DL00148 DS    0H                                                  0149 00359000
*         R8=R1 ;                       /* ADDR OF QUEUE HEADER      */ 00360000

*         R10=R8 -> WA1 ;               /* LOAD ADDR OF FIRST WE     */ 00362000

*         IF R10 ¬=0                    /* IS Q EMPTY                */ 00364000
*            THEN DO ;                  /* NO                        */ 00365000

*            RFY WESTD BASED (R10) ;    /* WE BASE                   */ 00368000
*            DO WHILE (WENEXT ¬=0 ) ;   /* FIND LAST WE              */ 00369000
         B     @DE00154                                            0154 00370000
@DL00154 DS    0H                                                  0155 00371000
*            R8=ADDR(WENEXT) ;          /* ADDR OF ADDR OF NEXT WE   */ 00372000

*            R10=WENEXT ;               /* RELOAD POINTER            */ 00374000

*            END ;                      /* FOUND LAST ONE            */ 00376000
@DE00154 L     @07,WENEXT(,R10)                                    0157 00377000

*            CS(R10,R9,R8->WA1) ;      /* DEQ THE W.E.               */ 00380000

*            BC(8,DEQ1) ;               /* SUCCESSFUL BRANCH         */ 00382000
         BC    8,DEQ1                                              0159 00383000
*            END ;                                                 0160 00384000
*            ELSE SW='0'B ;             /* QUEUE EMPTY               */ 00385000
         B     @RC00151                                            0161 00386000
@RF00151 NI    SW,B'11110111'                                      0161 00387000
*      END ;                            /* LOOP AROUND               */ 00388000
@RC00151 DS    0H                                                  0162 00389000
@DE00148 TM    SW,B'00001000'                                      0162 00390000
         BO    @DL00148                                            0162 00391000
*DEQ1 :R1=R10  ;                        /* ADDR OF THE WE DEQ        */ 00392000
DEQ1     LR    R1,R10                                              0163 00393000

*    /*                                                              */ 00028000
*    /*      ONE OF 4 FUNCTIONS MAY BE REQUESTED:                    */ 00029000
*    /*        ACB OPEN                                              */ 00030000
*    /*        ACB CLOSE                                             */ 00031000
*    /*        START LOGON                                           */ 00032000
*    /*        QUIESCE LOGON                                         */ 00033000
*    /*                                                              */ 00034000
*    /*      THE FOLLOWING CODE DETERMINE WHICH FUNCTION HAS BEEN    */ 00035000
*    /*      REQUESTED AND BRANCH TO THE PROPER ROUTINE TO PERFORM   */ 00036000
*    /*      THE FUNCTION                                            */ 00037000
*    /*                                                              */ 00038000
*      WERC=0 ;                        /* INITIALIZE RETURN CODE     */ 00039000

*      IF WECODE1F=FCVIAO              /* IS THIS ACB OPEN           */ 00042000
*         THEN CALL OPEN ;             /* YES, BRANCH TO IT          */ 00043000
         CLI   WECODE1F(R10),X'11'                                 0033 00044000

*             ELSE IF WECODE1F=FCVIAQ  /* NO, IS THIS QUIESCE LOGON  */ 00059000

*    /*                                                              */ 00065000
*    /*      THE FOLLOWING CODE CHECKS THE RETURN CODE SET BY        */ 00066000
*    /*      PERFORMING ROUTINE. IF IT IS NOT ZERO, THE W.E.         */ 00067000
*    /*      REPRESENTING THIS REQUEST IS DIRECTED TO THE SECOND     */ 00068000

*/*  *****************************************************************/ 00141000
*/*   IF THE SYNCHRONOUS (SYNC) QUEUE WAS NOT EMPTY, THE COMPARE     */ 00142000
*/*   AND SWAP USED TO ADD THE CLOSE ACB W.E. TO THAT QUEUE WILL     */ 00143000
*/*   FAIL (TEMPTR¬=0). IN THAT CASE, A WORK ELEMENT IS OBTAINED,    */ 00144000
*/*   ITS ADDRESS PUT INTO REG10, AND IT IS PLACED IN THE            */ 00145000
*/*   ASYNCHRONOUS QUEUE. WHEN IT IS PICKED OFF THE ASYNC QUEUE      */ 00146000
*/*   BY IKTCAS20, IKTCAS24 WILL BE RE-DRIVEN, WITH ITS ADDRESS IN   */ 00147000
*/*   REG10 AND IKTCAS24 WILL RE-TRY PUTTING THE CLOSE ACB W.E.      */ 00148000
*/*   ON THE SYNC QUEUE. IF THAT TRY FAILS AGAIN, THE WORK ELEMENT   */ 00149000
*/*   POINTED TO BY REG10 IS RE-USED, AND PLACED AGAIN ON THE ASYNC  */ 00150000
*/*   QUEUE TO CAUSE IKTCAS24 TO BE DRIVEN AGAIN.  THIS PROCESS      */ 00151000
*/*   CONTINUES UNTIL THE CLOSE ACB W.E. FOR TCAS CAN SUCCESSFULLY   */ 00152000
*/*   BE PLACED ON THE SYNC QUEUE.                                   */ 00153000
*/*  *****************************************************************/ 00154000
*                                                                  0087 00155000
*   IF TEMPPTR¬=0 THEN              /* IF CS NOT SUCCESSFUL          */ 00156000

*     DO;                           /* DO THE FOLLOWING              */ 00160000

*   RFY                                                            0117 00247000

./  ADD  SSI=02320510,NAME=IKTCAS32
         TITLE '***** IKTCAS32 - ADDRESS SPACE TERMINATION *****'       00001000
IKTCAS32 CSECT ,                                                   0001 00002000
@MAINENT DS    0H                                                  0001 00003000
         USING *,@15                                               0001 00004000
         B     @PROLOG                                             0001 00005000
         DC    AL1(16)                                             0001 00006000
         DC    C'IKTCAS32  80.232'                                 0001 00007000
         DROP  @15                                                      00008000
@PROLOG  STM   @14,@12,12(@13)                                     0001 00009000
         BALR  @12,0                                               0001 00010000
@PSTART  DS    0H                                                  0001 00011000
         USING @PSTART,@12                                         0001 00012000
         ST    @13,@SA00001+4                                      0001 00013000
         LA    @14,@SA00001                                        0001 00014000
         ST    @14,8(,@13)                                         0001 00015000
         LR    @13,@14                                             0001 00016000

*                                                                  0026 00023000
*ASTERM:                                                           0026 00024000
*   IF TWAUEIFC(2)=FCUITC           /* IS THIS RETRY, BECAUSE      0026 00025000
*                                      FOOTPRINT ALREAD SET          */ 00026000
*     THEN                                                         0026 00027000
ASTERM   CLI   TWAUEIFC+8(TWAPTR),33                               0026 00028000
         BNE   @RF00026                                            0026 00029000
*     DO;                           /* YES                           */ 00030000
*       CALL FREE;                  /* FREE MAIN IF GETMAINED        */ 00031000
         BAL   @14,FREE                                            0028 00032000
*     END;                                                         0029 00033000
*   ELSE                                                           0030 00034000
*     DO;                           /* NORMAL ENTRY                  */ 00035000
         B     @RC00026                                            0030 00036000
@RF00026 DS    0H                                                  0031 00037000
*       TWAUEIFC(2)=FCUITC;         /* SET FOOTPRINT IN ESTAI PARA   */ 00038000
         MVI   TWAUEIFC+8(TWAPTR),X'21'                            0031 00039000

         LA    @15,ASTERM                                          0032 00041000
         STCM  @15,7,TWAUERA+8(TWAPTR)                             0032 00042000
*       TWAUERRS(2)=EVAL(R13+4)->P; /* STORE SAVE AREA ADDRESS       */ 00043000
         LA    @15,4                                               0033 00044000

         L     @15,P(,@15)                                         0033 00046000
         ST    @15,TWAUERRS+8(,TWAPTR)                             0033 00047000
*     END;                                                         0034 00048000
*   RFY                                                            0035 00049000
*     TCAST BASED(TWATCAST);        /* GET TCAST ADDR                */ 00050000
@RC00026 DS    0H                                                  0036 00051000
*   RFY                                                            0036 00052000
*     WESTD BASED(R10);                                            0036 00053000
*   IF TCASUSEC¬=0                  /* IS USER COUNT NOT ZERO        */ 00054000
*     THEN                                                         0037 00055000
         L     @01,TWATCAST(,TWAPTR)                               0037 00056000
         LH    @15,TCASUSEC(,@01)                                  0037 00057000
         LTR   @15,@15                                             0037 00058000
         BZ    @RF00037                                            0037 00059000
*     DO;                           /* NO, PERFORM THE FUNCTION      */ 00060000
*       R8=TCASUSEC;                /* GET USER COUNT                */ 00061000
*                                                                  0039 00062000
         LR    R8,@15                                              0039 00063000
*       /*************************************************************/ 00064000
*       /*                                                           */ 00065000
*       /* GET STORAGE FOR A LIST OF ASCB ADDRESS                    */ 00066000
*       /*                                                           */ 00067000
*       /*************************************************************/ 00068000
*                                                                  0040 00069000
*       R8=(R8+4)*4;                /* CALCULATE GETMAIN LENGTH      */ 00070000
         LA    @15,4                                               0040 00071000

         SLA   @15,2                                               0040 00073000
         LR    R8,@15                                              0040 00074000
*       RFY                                                        0041 00075000
*        (R14,                                                     0041 00076000
*         R15,                                                     0041 00077000
*         R0,                                                      0041 00078000
*         R1) RSTD                  /* RESTRICT PARA REG             */ 00079000
*             ;                                                    0041 00080000
*       GEN CODE;                                                  0042 00081000
         GETMAIN R,LV=(8)         GETMAIN FOR LIST OF ASCB ADDR         00082000
*       AALISTP=R1;                 /* STORE POINTER                 */ 00083000
         ST    R1,AALISTP                                          0043 00084000
*       AALISTL=R8;                 /* STORE LENGTH                  */ 00085000
         ST    R8,AALISTL                                          0044 00086000

         L     @07,AALISTP                                         0045 00088000
         LR    R9,@07                                              0045 00089000
*       R8=FCUIAA;                  /* INDICATE EXTRACT ASCB ADDR    */ 00090000
*                                                                  0046 00091000
         LA    R8,50                                               0046 00092000
*       /*************************************************************/ 00093000
*       /*                                                           */ 00094000
*       /* CALL IKTCAS33 TO FILL IN ASCB ADDRESSES                   */ 00095000
*       /*                                                           */ 00096000
*       /*************************************************************/ 00097000
*                                                                  0047 00098000
*       GEN CODE;                                                  0047 00099000

*         R15,                                                     0048 00103000

         BNE   @RF00061                                            0061 00158000
