./  ADD  SSI=00330073,NAME=IKT93EST
         TITLE '*** IKT93EST: TSO/VTAM ESTAE FOR SVC 93 ***'            00001000
IKT93EST CSECT ,                                                01S0001 00002000
@MAINENT DS    0H                                               01S0001 00003000
         USING *,@15                                            01S0001 00004000
         B     @PROLOG                                          01S0001 00005000
         DC    AL1(16)                                          01S0001 00006000
         DC    C'IKT93EST  80.033'                              01S0001 00007000
         DROP  @15                                                      00008000
@PROLOG  BALR  @12,0                                            01S0001 00009000
@PSTART  DS    0H                                               01S0001 00010000
         USING @PSTART,@12                                      01S0001 00011000
RBPRFXLN EQU 64                                                         00012000
RBPRFLNA EQU 32                                                         00013000
PRBLEN   EQU 136                                                        00014000
SIRBLEN  EQU 200                                                        00015000
TIRBLEN  EQU 136                                                        00016000
IRBLEN   EQU 128                                                        00017000
SVRBLEN  EQU 224                                                        00018000
*                                      IKTASTPT              @ZMB6772*/ 00019000
*                                                               01S0077 00020000
*/********************************************************************/ 00021000
*/*                                                                  */ 00022000
*/* SEGMENT-                                                         */ 00023000
*/*       IKT93EST                                                   */ 00024000
*/*                                                                  */ 00025000
*/* FUNCTION-                                                        */ 00026000
*/*       MAINLINE                                                   */ 00027000
*/*                                                                  */ 00028000
*/********************************************************************/ 00029000
*                                                               01S0077 00030000
*   DO;                             /* BLOCK MAIN START OF MAIN BLOCK   00031000
*                                                            @ZMB6772*/ 00032000
*/*  LEAVE(MAIN) ON(REG0=12)                                         */ 00033000
*                                                               01S0078 00034000
*     IF(REG0=12) THEN                                          01S0078 00035000
         C     REG0,@CF02102                                    01S0078 00036000
         BE    @RT00078                                         01S0078 00037000
*       GOTO #BCM0001;              /* EXIT, NO SDWA PRESENT @ZMB6772*/ 00038000
*     STM(RTNREG,BASEREG,ESTAESA);  /* SAVE REGS IN ESTAE SAVE AREA  */ 00039000
         STM   RTNREG,BASEREG,ESTAESA(STORREG)                  01S0080 00040000
*     TSBPTR=ASCBTSB;               /* SET UP TSB ADDRESSABILITY     */ 00041000
         L     @15,ASCBPTR                                      01S0081 00042000
         L     TSBPTR,ASCBTSB(,@15)                             01S0081 00043000
*     SDWAPTR=REG1;                 /* SAVE ADDRESS OF SDWA          */ 00044000
         LR    SDWAPTR,REG1                                     01S0082 00045000
*     RBSECPTR=SDWAPARM;            /* ESTABLISH ADDRESSABILITY TO      00046000
*                                      EXTENDED SAVE AREA.           */ 00047000
         L     RBSECPTR,SDWAPARM(,SDWAPTR)                      01S0083 00048000
*     RFY                                                       01S0084 00049000
*       TVCS BASED(ESTTVCSP);       /*                       @ZMB6772*/ 00050000
*     IF SDWAPCHK='1'B&XSADMOVE='1'B THEN/* PGM CHECK DURING DATA       00051000
*                                      MOVE ?                        */ 00052000
         TM    SDWAPCHK(SDWAPTR),B'01000000'                    01S0085 00053000
         BNO   @RF00085                                         01S0085 00054000
         TM    XSADMOVE(RBSECPTR),B'01000000'                   01S0085 00055000
         BNO   @RF00085                                         01S0085 00056000
*       SDWACMPC=CMPLCODE;          /* YES, CHANGE COMPLETION CODE   */ 00057000
         MVC   SDWACMPC(3,SDWAPTR),CMPLCODE+1                   01S0086 00058000
*     IF XSAPTGT='0'B THEN          /* IF TPUT, THEN CLEAN UP TSB    */ 00059000
@RF00085 TM    XSAPTGT(RBSECPTR),B'10000000'                    01S0087 00060000
         BNZ   @RF00087                                         01S0087 00061000
*       CALL TSBCLEAN;              /* GO CLEAN UP PROPER TSB        */ 00062000
         BAL   @14,TSBCLEAN                                     01S0088 00063000
*     IF XSAIDENQ='1'B THEN         /* WAS AN ASID ENQ'ED IN IKTASTPT   00064000
*                                      ? YES, DEQUEUE THE ASID       */ 00065000
@RF00087 TM    XSAIDENQ(RBSECPTR),B'10000000'                   01S0089 00066000
         BNO   @RF00089                                         01S0089 00067000
*       DO;                                                     01S0090 00068000
*         RFY                                                   01S0091 00069000
*          (REG2,                                               01S0091 00070000
*           REG3) RSTD;                                         01S0091 00071000
*         XSAWD5='FF000000'X;       /* SET LIST FORM OF DEQ          */ 00072000
         MVC   XSAWD5(4,RBSECPTR),@CF02164                      01S0092 00073000
*         REG1=ADDR(XSAENQAD);      /* ADDRESS OF DEQ WORK AREA      */ 00074000
         LA    REG1,XSAENQAD(,RBSECPTR)                         01S0093 00075000
*         REG2=ADDR(QNAME);         /* GET QNAME ADDRESS FOR GEN     */ 00076000
         LA    REG2,QNAME                                       01S0094 00077000
*         REG3=ADDR(XSAASID);       /* GET RNAME ADDRESS FOR GEN     */ 00078000
         LA    REG3,XSAASID(,RBSECPTR)                          01S0095 00079000
*         GEN(DEQ ((REG2),(REG3),2,SYSTEM),RET=HAVE,MF=(E,(REG1)) );    00080000
         DEQ ((REG2),(REG3),2,SYSTEM),RET=HAVE,MF=(E,(REG1))            00081000
*       END;                                                    01S0097 00082000
*     RFY                                                       01S0098 00083000
*      (REG2,                                                   01S0098 00084000
*       REG3) UNRSTD;                                           01S0098 00085000
@RF00089 DS    0H                                               01S0099 00086000
*     SDWARCDE=SDWACWT;             /* INDICATE TO CONTINUE WITH        00087000
*                                      TERMINATION                   */ 00088000
         MVI   SDWARCDE(SDWAPTR),X'00'                          01S0099 00089000
*     SDWARTYA=0;                   /* CLEAR RETRY ADDRESS           */ 00090000
         SLR   @15,@15                                          01S0100 00091000
         ST    @15,SDWARTYA(,SDWAPTR)                           01S0100 00092000
*     LM(RTNREG,BASEREG,ESTAESA);   /* RESTORE REGISTERS             */ 00093000
         LM    RTNREG,BASEREG,ESTAESA(STORREG)                  01S0101 00094000
*   END;                            /* END                           */ 00095000
*#BCM0001:                                                      01S0103 00096000
*   ;                               /* END OF MAIN BLOCK     @ZMB6772*/ 00097000
#BCM0001 DS    0H                                               01S0104 00098000
*/********************************************************************/ 00099000
*/* THE FOLLOWING CODE IS REACHED BY ANY ?LEAVE (MAIN) MACRO         */ 00100000
*/********************************************************************/ 00101000
*                                                               01S0104 00102000
*   RETURN CODE(0);                 /* RETURN TO RTM                 */ 00103000
         SLR   @15,@15                                          01S0104 00104000
@EL00001 DS    0H                                               01S0104 00105000
@EF00001 DS    0H                                               01S0104 00106000
@ER00001 BR    @14                                              01S0104 00107000
         EJECT                                                          00108000
*                                                               01S0105 00109000
*/********************************************************************/ 00110000
*/*                                                                  */ 00111000
*/* SUBROUTINE-                                                      */ 00112000
*/*      TSBCLEAN                                                    */ 00113000
*/*                                                                  */ 00114000
*/* FUNCTION-                                                        */ 00115000
*/*      RESET TSB FIELDS FOR TGET/TPUT/TPG                          */ 00116000
*/*                                                                  */ 00117000
*/********************************************************************/ 00118000
*                                                               01S0105 00119000
*TSBCLEAN:                                                      01S0105 00120000
*   PROC OPTIONS(NOSAVEAREA,NOSAVE);                            01S0105 00121000
TSBCLEAN DS    0H                                               01S0106 00122000
*   XSASAVEA=RTNREG;                /* SAVE RETURN ADDRESS           */ 00123000
         ST    RTNREG,XSASAVEA(,RBSECPTR)                       01S0106 00124000
*   GEN SETS(RTNREG,ENTRYREG,REG0,REG1) REFS(PSALITA,FLC);      01S0107 00125000
*                                   /* GET THE LOCAL LOCK            */ 00126000
         SETLOCK OBTAIN,TYPE=LOCAL,MODE=UNCOND,REGS=USE,               -00127000
               RELATED=(TSB,TSBCLEAN(RETURN))                           00128000
*   IF TSBPTR¬=0&TSBCTCB=CURNTTCB THEN/* IF FOREGROUND JOB, THEN DOES   00129000
*                                      THIS TASK 'OWN' THE TSB ?     */ 00130000
         SLR   @15,@15                                          01S0108 00131000
         CR    TSBPTR,@15                                       01S0108 00132000
         BE    @RF00108                                         01S0108 00133000
         L     @08,CVTPTR                                       01S0108 00134000
         L     @07,CVTTCBP(,@08)                                01S0108 00135000
         CLC   TSBCTCB(4,TSBPTR),CURNTTCB(@07)                  01S0108 00136000
         BNE   @RF00108                                         01S0108 00137000
*     DO;                           /* PROCESS THIS TASK OWNS TSB    */ 00138000
*       TSBOWIP='0'B;               /* CLEAR 'OWAIT IN PROGRESS      */ 00139000
         NI    TSBOWIP(TSBPTR),B'11011111'                      01S0110 00140000
*       TSBCTCB=0;                  /* SET TO NOT 'OWN' TSB          */ 00141000
         ST    @15,TSBCTCB(,TSBPTR)                             01S0111 00142000
*       IF TSBWOWIP='1'B THEN       /* ANYBODY WAITING ?             */ 00143000
         TM    TSBWOWIP(TSBPTR),B'00010000'                     01S0112 00144000
         BNO   @RF00112                                         01S0112 00145000
*         DO;                       /* YES                           */ 00146000
*           TSBWOWIP='0'B;          /* CLEAR OWAIT IN PROGRESS IND   */ 00147000
         NI    TSBWOWIP(TSBPTR),B'11101111'                     01S0114 00148000
*           RFY                                                 01S0115 00149000
*             REG2 RSTD;                                        01S0115 00150000
*           REG2=STORREG;           /* SAVE ESTAE SAVE AREA  @ZMB6772*/ 00151000
         LR    REG2,STORREG                                     01S0116 00152000
*           STORREG=NDISPBIT;       /* INDICATE THAT NON-DISPATCH-      00153000
*                                      ABILITY BIT TO RESET IS OWAIT    00154000
*                                                            @ZMB6772*/ 00155000
         LA    STORREG,1024                                     01S0117 00156000
*           REG0=ASCBASID*65536|ALLTASKS;/* ALL TASKS WILL BE RESET  */ 00157000
         L     @15,ASCBPTR                                      01S0118 00158000
         LH    REG0,ASCBASID(,@15)                              01S0118 00159000
         N     REG0,@CF02189                                    01S0118 00160000
         SLA   REG0,16                                          01S0118 00161000
         O     REG0,@CF00049                                    01S0118 00162000
*           REG1=RESET;             /* INDICATE RESET VS. SET        */ 00163000
         L     REG1,RESET                                       01S0119 00164000
*           CALL STATUS;            /* DRIVE SUSPENDED TASKS         */ 00165000
         L     @08,SCVTSPTR(,@08)                               01S0120 00166000
         L     @15,SCVTSTAT(,@08)                               01S0120 00167000
         BALR  @14,@15                                          01S0120 00168000
*           STORREG=REG2;           /* RESTORE SAVE AREA ADDRESS        00169000
*                                                            @ZMB6772*/ 00170000
         LR    STORREG,REG2                                     01S0121 00171000
*           RFY                                                 01S0122 00172000
*             REG2 UNRSTD;                                      01S0122 00173000
*         END;                      /* END, THIS TASK OWNS TSB       */ 00174000
*       GEN SETS(RTNREG,ENTRYREG,REG0,REG1) REFS(PSALITA,FLC);  01S0124 00175000
@RF00112 DS    0H                                               01S0124 00176000
*                                   /* RELEASE LOCAL LOCK            */ 00177000
         SETLOCK RELEASE,TYPE=LOCAL,REGS=USE,                          -00178000
               RELATED=(TSB,TSBCLEAN(ENTRY));                           00179000
*     END;                          /* END 'THIS TASKS OWNS TSB'     */ 00180000
*   ELSE                            /* TASK DOES NOT OWN TSB         */ 00181000
*     DO;                           /* PROCESS OTHER TASK OWNS TSB      00182000

         B     @RC00108                                         01S0126 00184000

*       WORK1REG=XSAASID&NEDMASK;   /* GET ASID, NEDIT FLAG OFF 01S0127 00186000

*       IF WORK1REG¬=0&             /* ASID SPECIFIED        @ZMB6188*/ 00190000

         LTR   @15,@15                                          01S0128 00203000
         BZ    @RF00128                                         01S0128 00204000
*         DO;                       /* PROCESS CROSS MEMORY TPUT     */ 00205000
*           RFY                                                 01S0130 00206000
*             WORK2REG RSTD;        /* RESTRICT WORK REGISTERS  01S0130 00207000
*                                                            @ZMB6188*/ 00208000
*           WORK1REG=TVCSINDS;      /* FIRST OPERAND FOR CS          */ 00209000
         L     WORK1REG,TVCSINDS(,@15)                          01S0131 00210000
*CSLOOP:                                                        01S0132 00211000
*           WORK2REG=WORK1REG;      /* THIRD OPERAND FOR CS          */ 00212000
CSLOOP   LR    WORK2REG,WORK1REG                                01S0132 00213000
*           IF TVCSTGRC='1'B|ESTSCHED=0 THEN/* IF TARGET HAS GIVEN UP   00214000
*                                      TVCS CONTROL, OR IKTXMTPT HAS    00215000
*                                      NOT BEEN SCHEDULED    @ZMB6772*/ 00216000
         L     @15,ESTTVCSP-1(,RBSECPTR)                        01S0133 00217000

*             DO;                   /* CLEAN UP CROSS MEMORY TPUT    */ 00223000
*               GEN SETS(RTNREG,ENTRYREG,REG0,REG1) REFS(PSALITA,FLC);  00224000
*                                   /* OBTAIN CMS LOCK               */ 00225000
         SETLOCK OBTAIN,TYPE=CMS,MODE=UNCOND,REGS=USE,                 -00226000
               RELATED=(TARGET-TSB)                                     00227000
*               CALL TERMSTAT;      /* CHECK TERMINAL STATUS         */ 00228000
         BAL   @14,TERMSTAT                                     01S0136 00229000
*               IF XSARC¬=TERMCNCL THEN/* OTHER TERMINAL STILL THERE?*/ 00230000

*                 DO;               /* RESET TARGET TSB              */ 00233000
*                   TSBXCSAP=0;     /* CLEAR POINTER TO TVCS         */ 00234000
         SLR   @15,@15                                          01S0139 00235000

         ST    @15,TSBXCSAP(,@08)                               01S0139 00237000
*                   TSBWTJID=0;     /* CLEAR CALLING ASID FIELD      */ 00238000

*                   TSBWTCB=0;      /* CLEAR CALLING TCB FIELD       */ 00240000

*                 END;              /* END, RESET TARGET TSB         */ 00242000
*               GEN SETS(RTNREG,ENTRYREG,REG0,REG1) REFS(PSALITA,FLC);  00243000
@RF00137 DS    0H                                               01S0143 00244000
*                                   /* RELEASE CMS AND LOCAL LOCKS   */ 00245000

         SETLOCK RELEASE,TYPE=LOCAL,REGS=USE,RELATED=(CMS-LOCK)         00247000
*               CALL FREESTOR;      /* NOW FREE CSA STORAGE          */ 00248000
         BAL   @14,FREESTOR                                     01S0144 00249000
*             END;                  /* END TARGET RELINQUISHED  01S0145 00250000
*                                      CONTROL 'DO'                  */ 00251000
*           ELSE                    /* TARGET HAS TVCS CONTROL       */ 00252000
*             DO;                   /* SET SOURCE RELEASES CONTROL   */ 00253000
         B     @RC00133                                         01S0146 00254000
@RF00133 DS    0H                                               01S0147 00255000
*               GEN SETS(WORK2REG) REFS(SOURCERC)(O  WORK2REG,SOURCERC) 00256000
*                   ;               /* TURN ON TVCSRCRC              */ 00257000
         O  WORK2REG,SOURCERC                                           00258000
*               CS(WORK1REG,WORK2REG,TVCSINDS);/* DO THE COMPARE &      00259000
*                                      SWAP                          */ 00260000
         L     @03,ESTTVCSP-1(,RBSECPTR)                        01S0148 00261000
         CS    WORK1REG,@02,TVCSINDS(@03)                       01S0148 00262000
*               BC(NE,CSLOOP);      /* CONTINUE LOOP IF CS FAILED    */ 00263000
         BC    7,CSLOOP                                         01S0149 00264000
*               GEN SETS(RTNREG,ENTRYREG,REG0,REG1) REFS(PSALITA,FLC)   00265000
*                   (SETLOCK RELEASE,TYPE=LOCAL,REGS=USE,RELATED=(TSB)) 00266000
*                   ;               /* RELEASE LOCAL LOCK            */ 00267000
         SETLOCK RELEASE,TYPE=LOCAL,REGS=USE,RELATED=(TSB)              00268000
*             END;                  /* END OF CS FOR SETTING TVCSRCRC*/ 00269000
*           RFY                                                 01S0152 00270000
*             WORK2REG UNRSTD;      /*                       @ZA19923*/ 00271000

*                                   /* RELEASE LOCAL LOCK     @ZA19923* 00278000

*/********************************************************************/ 00291000
*/*                                                                  */ 00292000
*/* SUBROUTINE-                                                      */ 00293000
*/*      FREESTOR                                                    */ 00294000
*/*                                                                  */ 00295000
*/* FUNCTION-                                                        */ 00296000
*/*      COMPLETE CROSS-MEMORY POST, AND FREE CSA AREA               */ 00297000
*/*                                                                  */ 00298000
*/********************************************************************/ 00299000
*                                                               01S0158 00300000
*FREESTOR:                                                      01S0158 00301000
*   PROC OPTIONS(NOSAVEAREA,NOSAVE);                            01S0158 00302000
FREESTOR DS    0H                                               01S0159 00303000
*   XSASAVEB=RTNREG;                /* SAVE RETURN ADDRESS           */ 00304000
         ST    RTNREG,XSASAVEB(,RBSECPTR)                       01S0159 00305000
*   GEN CODE SETS(REG1) REFS(CVTPTR,CVTSPOST,CVTMAP)(SPOST );/* ISSUE   00306000
*                                      SPOST                         */ 00307000
         SPOST                                                          00308000
*   RFY                                                         01S0161 00309000
*    (REG2,                                                     01S0161 00310000
*     REG7,                                                     01S0161 00311000
*     REG8) RSTD;                                               01S0161 00312000
*   REG2=TVCSSRBA;                  /* GET ADDR FOR SRB FREEMAIN     */ 00313000
         L     @15,ESTTVCSP-1(,RBSECPTR)                        01S0162 00314000
         LA    @15,0(,@15)                                      01S0162 00315000
         L     REG2,TVCSSRBA-1(,@15)                            01S0162 00316000
         LA    REG2,0(,REG2)                                    01S0162 00317000
*   REG7=TVCSGMSZ;                  /* GET SIZE FOR TVCS FREEMAIN    */ 00318000
         LH    REG7,TVCSGMSZ(,@15)                              01S0163 00319000
*   REG8=ESTTVCSP;                  /* GET ADDR FOR TVCS FREEMAIN       00320000
*                                                            @ZMB6772*/ 00321000
         LR    REG8,@15                                         01S0164 00322000
*   GEN CODE SETS(RTNREG,ENTRYREG,REG0,REG1) REFS(PSALITA,FLC); 01S0165 00323000
*                                   /* OBTAIN SALLOC LOCK            */ 00324000
         SETLOCK OBTAIN,TYPE=SALLOC,MODE=UNCOND,REGS=USE,              -00325000
               RELATED=(TVCS,SRB)                                       00326000
*   IF REG2¬=0 THEN                 /* IS THERE AN SRB ?             */ 00327000
         LTR   REG2,REG2                                        01S0166 00328000
         BZ    @RF00166                                         01S0166 00329000
*     DO;                           /* YES, FREE IT                  */ 00330000
*       REG0=LENGTH(SRB);           /* GET LENGTH FOR FREEMAIN       */ 00331000
         LA    REG0,44                                          01S0168 00332000
*       GEN SETS(RTNREG,ENTRYREG,REG1,REG3,REG4) REFS(CVTSPSA,CVTMAP,   00333000
*           WSAGGMFM,WSAG,CVTGLMN);                             01S0169 00334000
         FREEMAIN RU,LV=(0),A=(REG2),SP=239,KEY=0,                     -00335000

*     END;                                                      01S0170 00337000
*   REG0=REG7;                      /* GET LENGTH OF TVCS            */ 00338000

*   GEN CODE SETS(RTNREG,ENTRYREG,REG1,REG3,REG4) REFS(CVTSPSA,CVTMAP,  00340000

*   GEN CODE SETS(RTNREG,ENTRYREG,REG0,REG1) REFS(PSALITA,FLC); 01S0173 00344000

*   RFY                                                         01S0174 00346000
*     REG2 UNRSTD;                                              01S0174 00347000

         EJECT                                                          00354000

*/* SUBROUTINE-                                                      */ 00358000
*/*      TERMSTAT                                                    */ 00359000
*/*                                                                  */ 00360000
*/* FUNCTION-                                                        */ 00361000
*/*      DETERMINE STATUS OF TARGET TERMINAL                         */ 00362000
*/*                                                                  */ 00363000

*                                                               01S0177 00365000
*TERMSTAT:                                                      01S0177 00366000
*   PROC OPTIONS(NOSAVEAREA,NOSAVE);                            01S0177 00367000
TERMSTAT DS    0H                                               01S0178 00368000
*   XSASAVEB=RTNREG;                /* SAVE RETURN ADDRESS           */ 00369000
         ST    RTNREG,XSASAVEB(,RBSECPTR)                       01S0178 00370000
*   XSARC=TERMCNCL;                 /* INITIALIZE RETURN CODE        */ 00371000
         MVI   XSARC(RBSECPTR),X'14'                            01S0179 00372000
*   RFY                                                         01S0180 00373000
*     ASCB BASED(ASVTENTY(XSAASID));/* THE ASVT POINTS TO THE ASCB S    00374000
*                                      ADDRESS. BASE THE ASCB ON THE    00375000
*                                      ENTRY SPECIFIED BY THE ASID   */ 00376000
*   IF CVTTCASP¬=0 THEN             /* IS TSO/VTAM UP ? YES IT IS    */ 00377000
         SLR   @15,@15                                          01S0181 00378000
         L     @04,CVTPTR                                       01S0181 00379000
         C     @15,CVTTCASP(,@04)                               01S0181 00380000
         BE    @RF00181                                         01S0181 00381000
*     IF ASVTAVAL(XSAASID)='0'B THEN/* CHECK IF ASID SLOT IN ASVT       00382000
*                                      INDICATES IT IS ASSIGNED      */ 00383000
         LH    @11,XSAASID(,RBSECPTR)                           01S0182 00384000
         SLA   @11,2                                            01S0182 00385000
         L     @04,ASVTPTR(,@04)                                01S0182 00386000
         ALR   @11,@04                                          01S0182 00387000
         TM    ASVTAVAL-4(@11),B'10000000'                      01S0182 00388000
         BNZ   @RF00182                                         01S0182 00389000
*       DO;                                                     01S0183 00390000
*         TSBPTR=ASCBTSB;           /* DEFINE TSB POINTER OF TARGET     00391000
*                                      ADDRESS SPACE                 */ 00392000
         LH    @11,XSAASID(,RBSECPTR)                           01S0184 00393000
         SLA   @11,2                                            01S0184 00394000
         L     @04,ASVTENTY-4(@11,@04)                          01S0184 00395000
         L     TSBPTR,ASCBTSB(,@04)                             01S0184 00396000
*         RFY                                                   01S0185 00397000
*           ASCB BASED(ASCBPTR);    /* NOW RE-BASE ASCB FOR THIS        00398000
*                                      ADDRESS SPACE                 */ 00399000
*         IF TSBPTR¬=0&TSBWTJID=ASCBASID THEN/* IS THE ASID STORED      00400000
*                                      THIS ASID?                    */ 00401000
         CR    TSBPTR,@15                                       01S0186 00402000
         BE    @RF00186                                         01S0186 00403000
         L     @15,ASCBPTR                                      01S0186 00404000
         LH    @15,ASCBASID(,@15)                               01S0186 00405000
         N     @15,@CF02189                                     01S0186 00406000
         CH    @15,TSBWTJID(,TSBPTR)                            01S0186 00407000
         BNE   @RF00186                                         01S0186 00408000
*           IF TSBCANC='0'B THEN    /* IF SESSION HAS BEEN CANCELLED */ 00409000
         TM    TSBCANC(TSBPTR),B'00000100'                      01S0187 00410000
         BNZ   @RF00187                                         01S0187 00411000
*             XSARC=CONTINUE;       /* CONTINUE                      */ 00412000
         MVI   XSARC(RBSECPTR),X'00'                            01S0188 00413000
*       END;                                                    01S0189 00414000
@RF00187 DS    0H                                               01S0189 00415000
@RF00186 DS    0H                                               01S0190 00416000
*   RTNREG=XSASAVEB;                /* RESTORE RETURN ADDRESS        */ 00417000
@RF00182 DS    0H                                               01S0190 00418000
@RF00181 L     RTNREG,XSASAVEB(,RBSECPTR)                       01S0190 00419000
*   END TERMSTAT;                                               01S0191 00420000
@EL00004 DS    0H                                               01S0191 00421000
@EF00004 DS    0H                                               01S0191 00422000
@ER00004 BR    @14                                              01S0191 00423000
